<p class="western">And Dhimmi woman also has no "Sanctity" (حرمة) like the slave woman.<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171101193549/http://alsafwh.net/library/vblibrary/alwasael/wasael-20/v10.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wasail-us-Shia (link)</a>:</p>
